      'about_us_text': 'PAWIVA is a simple yet meaningful app designed to help you track the time you spend with your pet.\n\nWhether it\'s a walk in the park, playtime at home, cozy naps together, or just sitting side by side.\n\nPAWIVA records these precious moments and turns them into weekly, monthly, and yearly insights. But it\'s not just about tracking.\n\nPAWIVA also lets you share your special moments effortlessly as a story on Instagram or a cute summary for your friends. Because every minute has its pawprint.',
      'privacy_text': 'Last Updated: 01.05.2026\n\nPawiva ("the App", "we", "our", "us") values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the App. By using Pawiva, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.\n\n1. Information We Collect\nWe may collect the following types of information:\n\n- Activity Data: Information you provide when recording pet-related activities (e.g., walking time, playtime, sleeping time).\n- Account Information: If you create an account, we may collect your email address or other identifiers you provide.\n- Device Information: Basic technical information such as device type, operating system, app version, and usage statistics.\n\nPawiva does not collect or process health-related data (e.g., vaccinations, medical treatments, or medical history).\n\n2. How We Use Your Information\nWe use your information for the following purposes:\n\n- To provide, operate, and improve the App.\n- To generate analytics and insights about your pet activities.\n- To allow you to share selected activity data on social media platforms (if you choose to do so).\n- To communicate with you regarding updates, support, or important notices.\n\n3. Sharing of Information\nWe do not sell or rent your personal data to third parties. We may share your information only in the following circumstances:\n\n- With service providers who support our operations (e.g., analytics or cloud hosting providers).\n- If required by law or to protect our legal rights.\n- With your consent, when you choose to share your activity data on third-party platforms (e.g., Instagram).\n\n4. Data Storage & Security\n- Your data is stored securely using industry-standard practices.\n- While we take reasonable measures to protect your information, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure.\n- You are responsible for keeping your account credentials confidential.\n\n5. Your Rights\nDepending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:\n\n- Access the personal data we hold about you.\n- Request correction or deletion of your data.\n- Withdraw your consent for data processing (where applicable).\n\nTo exercise these rights, please contact us at csknrmk.aydn@icloud.com.\n\n6. Children\'s Privacy\nPawiva is not directed at children under the age of 13 (or the age of digital consent in your country). We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.\n\n7. Changes to This Privacy Policy\nWe may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted within the App, and the updated policy will become effective upon posting.\n\n8. Contact Us\nIf you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:\nEmail: csknrmk.aydn@icloud.com\nAddress: -',
      'terms_of_use_text': 'Last Updated: 01.05.2026\n\nBy downloading, installing, or using Pawiva ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use ("Terms"). If you do not agree with these Terms, you must not use the App.\n\n1. Service Description\nPawiva is a mobile application that allows users to record and track the time spent with their pets (such as walking, playing, sleeping together), view analytics over weekly, monthly, and yearly periods, and optionally share this information on social media platforms.\n\n2. Eligibility & Use of the App\n- The App is provided solely for personal, non-commercial use.\n- You agree to use the App in compliance with all applicable laws and regulations.\n- Your account is personal and must not be shared with third parties.\n\n3. Data & Privacy\n- Pawiva collects activity data you record within the App (e.g., walking time, playtime, sleeping time).\n- Pawiva does not collect medical or health-related data (e.g., vaccinations, treatments, medical history).\n- The processing of personal data is governed by our Privacy Policy, which should be read together with these Terms.\n\n4. Intellectual Property\n- All rights, titles, and interests in and to the App, including but not limited to software, design, graphics, and logos, are owned by Pawiva or its licensors.\n- You may not copy, distribute, modify, reverse-engineer, or exploit any part of the App without prior written consent.\n\n5. User Content\n- You are solely responsible for the content you create, upload, or share via the App.\n- By posting or sharing content, you grant Pawiva a limited, non-exclusive license to use such content solely for operating and improving the App.\n\n6. Disclaimer of Warranties\n- The App is provided "as is" and "as available."\n- Pawiva does not guarantee uninterrupted, error-free, or secure operation of the App.\n- Pawiva disclaims all liability for damages arising from your use of the App, to the maximum extent permitted by law.\n\n7. Third-Party Services & Links\nThe App may contain links to third-party services or platforms. Pawiva is not responsible for the availability, accuracy, or content of such third-party services.\n\n8. Modifications\nPawiva reserves the right to update or change these Terms at any time. Updated Terms will be effective once posted within the App. Continued use of the App after such updates constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.\n\n9. Termination\nPawiva may suspend or terminate your access to the App if you violate these Terms or engage in any prohibited activities.\n\n10. Governing Law\nThese Terms shall be governed and construed in accordance with the laws of Republic of Turkey without regard to conflict of law provisions. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Istanbul, Turkey.\n\n11. Contact Us\nFor questions or concerns about these Terms, please contact us:\nEmail: csknrmk.aydn@icloud.com\nAddress: -',
